and events of great magnitude.

4
00:00:26,120 --> 00:00:30,560
Clouds gathered
over the mighty Commonwealth:

5
00:00:30,880 --> 00:00:35,640
Poland, Lithuania and Ukraine
united under the rule of Wladislaw IV

6
